001	GEN	004	003	One day, Cain brought a gift to give to God. He brought some food from his garden.
001	GEN	004	004	And Abel brought a gift to give to God too. He gave God some of his young sheep and goats. They were the first ones born to their mothers. Abel brought the best bits of meat from those sheep and goats. And God was happy with Abel, and with his gift.
