044	ACT	003	005	So the man looked at them. He thought, “I reckon these 2 men will give me some money.”
044	ACT	003	006	But Peter said, “I haven’t got any money. But I have got something really good for you. Jesus Christ, the man from Nazareth, has the power to make you better, so I’m talking to you with his power, and I tell you, get up and walk.”
