044	ACT	027	024	and he said, ‘Paul, don’t be frightened. You have to go and stand in front of Caesar, the big boss in Rome. And God will be good to all the other men that are with you on this ship too. None of them will die.’
044	ACT	027	025	Listen friends, don’t be frightened. I believe that God will help us, just like that angel told me.
